      <section eId="sec_159_K">
        <num>159-K</num>
        <heading>Monitoring and evaluation</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_159_K__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>determining the effectiveness of recipients' administrative\noperations, organizational structure, planning and programming, self\nevaluation, and general decision making; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_159_K__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>reviewing the recipients' compliance with federal and state law\nand regulation.\n  2. For purposes of evaluations conducted under this section,\nrecipients shall make available to the secretary, or any duly authorized\nofficer or employee of the department, appropriate books, documents,\npapers and records for examination, copying or mechanical reproduction\non or off the premises of the recipient upon a reasonable request\ntherefor.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
